OL,3,CDrought declared in the Midlands -
OL,4,Chere's what it means for you
OL,6,FThe West and East Midlands have
OL,7,Fofficially moved into drought, with
OL,8,Fsome river flows at their lowest since
OL,9,FJune 1976.
OL,11,FAcross England, rainfall was 20% less
OL,12,Fthan the long-term average for June.
OL,13,FIt was also the hottest on record for
OL,14,FEngland, with three heatwaves driving
OL,15,Funusually high demand for water.
