OL,3,CDrought declared in the Midlands -
OL,4,Chere's what it means for you
OL,6,FAs the UK braces for a possible fourth
OL,7,Fheatwave later this month, there are
OL,8,Fserious concerns about water demand
OL,9,Fand reduced reservoir levels. Millions
OL,10,Fof people across the Midlands could be
OL,11,Faffected.
OL,13,FThe National Drought Group met today
OL,14,F(Tuesday 15 July) to officially
OL,15,Fdeclare a drought. It says that
OL,16,Fwithout further rain, extra measures
OL,17,Fwill be needed to conserve water
OL,18,Fsupplies.
